OL,5,G0330 Drop The Dead Donkey
OL,6,     FAn execution proves less telegenic
OL,7,     Fthan Damien had hoped. Closer to
OL,8,     Fhome, his coverage of an animal
OL,9,     Fliberation raid lacks glamour
OL,10,     Funtil he takes charge and turns it
OL,11,     Finto a dog's dinner - literally.
OL,12,G0400 Drop The Dead Donkey
OL,13,     FThe news team achieves its
OL,14,     Fultimate aim and, as well as
OL,15,     Fgetting a late extension to the
OL,16,     Fbar, they secure an interview with
OL,17,     Fthe Prime Minister
OL,18,G0430 Stereo Underground
OL,19,     FRichard Latto presents alternative
OL,20,     Fanthems from a music community
OL,21,     Fwith attitude.
