OL,5,G0530 Jack Hargreaves' Old Country
OL,6,     FJack Hargreaves is stocking his
OL,7,     Friver with native brown trout. He
OL,8,     Flaments the widespread loss of
OL,9,     Fponds in the countryside, but
OL,10,     Ffinds one that is thriving.
